Still in development.

Ever get annoyed by how fast Cardmarket logs you out, and therefore resets your filters on every page navigation?

This add-on allows you to:
- Remember your login;
- Set default language filters;
- Hides languages you have no use for;
- Adds quick filters to each listing page: Minimum condition, Is first edition, Is reverse holo, and Language;
- Option to force a 2 column grid layout for search results on mobile;
- Show deviating prices to alert for price surges;
- Adds Dark mode support (force Dark mode, force Light mode, or automatically based on device setting);
- Highlights difficult to search for terms, like Ex, GX, V, VMAX;
- Shows games browser on user their offers (quick switch between Pok√©mon / One Piece stock for a user);
- Adds From prices per condition;
- Syncs quick filter selections with the 'Sell' form. Ie.: select Minimum condition = 'Good', to have the selling form autoselect 'Good' as well;
- And more! (user blocklist shortcut, price shortcuts on sell forms (From, 1D/7D/30D AVG))
